{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b092a334de","title":"祝贺日内瓦会议达成印度支那停战协议致胡志明电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"99b26f71f7","index":0,"year":1954,"month":7,"day":23,"articleId":"b092a334de"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"1ce1fd9db4","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为祝贺日内瓦会议达成印度支那停战协议给越南民主共和国政府主席胡志明的电报。"}],"contents":[{"id":"dbc00e00b6","type":"title","text":"祝贺日内瓦会议达成印度支那停战协议致胡志明电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de"},{"id":"1ce1fd9db4","type":"paragraph","text":"越南民主共和国政府主席胡志明同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de"},{"id":"72a5df8ad5","type":"paragraph","text":"当印度支那停战问题和政治问题达成协议之际，我代表中国人民和中华人民共和国政府向兄弟般的越南人民、越南民主共和国政府和您致以最衷心最热烈的祝贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de"},{"id":"0e0b54434f","type":"paragraph","text":"越南民主共和国代表团在日内瓦会议上，代表着为民族独立机自由而英勇斗争并已取得辉煌胜利的越南人民的和平愿望，努力争取恢复印度支那和平，终于达成协议，这是越南人民的又一重大胜利，这一胜利有助于促进亚洲的集体和平与安全，有助于进一步缓和国际紧张局势。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de"},{"id":"1eed94dca2","type":"paragraph","text":"全中国的人民将与越南人民一道为保证与争取协议的彻底实现，为维护和巩固亚洲及全世界的和平与安全而努力。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de"},{"id":"312a40582b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de"},{"id":"cffa5d8efe","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年七月二十三日于北京","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de"}],"page":{"id":"bc21b7580a","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b092a334de","start":165,"end":165}}}},"__N_SSG":true}